{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "/nodes/sop/DASH--vector_components_didactic-1.0/DASH-didactic.svg", "type": "node", "context": "sop", "internal": "vector_components_didactic", "version": "1.0", "namespace": "DASH"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Vector Components"], "extent": [34, 54]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Interactive demonstration of a Position Vector, its components, and how to make a relative position."], "extent": [54, 163]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [163, 178], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Explore insights about the ", {"scheme": "Wp", "value": "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Position_(geometry)", "type": "link", "text": ["Position Vector"], "exists": true}, " in an interactive way. Instructions to manipulate visualization directly in the viewport:"], "extent": [178, 338]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": ["Set the Display flag on this node and click the button ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Create Interactive Geo"]}, "."], "extent": [338, 424]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": ["Select the created ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/kinefx--rigpose", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/kinefx--rigpose.html"}, " node and with the mouse over the viewport, press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " to bring up its KineFX viewerstate in the viewport and manipulate the vector visualization this way."], "extent": [424, 633]}], "container": true}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 0, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/nodes/sop/DASH--vector_components_didactic-1.0/DASH-help_didactic_start.gif", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [633, 685]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "